on_offseat=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:white; padding: 0% 4% 2% 4%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-visible-phone\" ><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 60px 0 0 0;\"><\/div><h4><b>Chief Financial Officer<\/b><\/h4>\n<p>We are growing at an incredible pace and are now looking for a Chief Financial Official (CFO) to join the team. In this pivotal role, you will take ownership of DIVD.fund&#8217;s financial operations, ensuring both organizational efficiency and compliance. Additionally, you will collaborate closely with the CEO to drive our fundraising efforts and manage our funding program. The CFO will report to the CEO.<\/p>\n<p><b>Key Responsibilities<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Manage all accounting activities \u2014 both internally and with third parties \u2014 to maintain the highest standards of integrity, completeness, and accuracy.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Formulating, implementing, and monitoring compliance within and through accounting policies.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Managing the month-end close process and producing monthly management accounts and reports with strict adherence to organizational timelines.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Ensuring compliance with relevant statutory, tax, auditing, and external reporting requirements.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Oversight of finance-related regulatory processes, including safeguarding, charity requirements, and supporting the provision of financial information for regulatory projects.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Work with the CEO in preparing and monitoring performance against forecasts and budgets, providing analysis and strategic insight.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>Qualifications<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Have an interest in volunteer organizations and ideally have experience in working for one<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Have a keen or growing interest in charity activities.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Have experience working within the finance department or regulated financial services organization, ideally in a team lead or more senior position, with demonstrable experience in managing a finance team.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Are a fully qualified accountant with post-qualification experience and statutory reporting knowledge.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Experience in audit, financial reporting, financial control, or regulatory reporting.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Thrive in an ever-changing, highly charitable work environment where the answer to a question may not be immediately available.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Are a self-starter, capable of working autonomously with minimal supervision, and a team player at heart.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><b>What we offer<\/b><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A chance to work with a dynamic, mission-driven team dedicated to making the internet safer.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A flexible, remote work environment.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Opportunities for professional growth and impact in a global organization.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A vibrant and dynamic organizational culture<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">An extensive network, being part of our DIVD family community.<\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Regular meet ups and special events.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[vc_row_inner inner_container=&#8221;true&#8221; no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column_inner fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;]<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 20px 0 0 0;\"><a  class=\"x-btn x-btn-pill x-btn-regular x-btn-block\"  href=\"https:\/\/form.jotform.com\/223184612605350\"  target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"   data-options=\"thumbnail: ''\"><span style=\"colo